ruok.quality.globalquality.tooltip: Adjusts settings that affect render distance, graphics quality, and particle effects.
ruok.quality.autoquality.tooltip: This setting automatically adjusts your graphics quality based on your computer's performance. It checks every 30 seconds for a total of 6 times.
ruok.quality.renderdistance.tooltip: Based on your settings, it creates a cube with your specified radius and only renders entities inside that cube.
ruok.quality.renderentity.tooltip: Based on your settings for 'Render Entity Distance,' it determines the number of entities currently being rendered.
